data.title: Love Connie
data.text:
American actor

Love Connie is the stage name of John Cantwell, an American drag queen, actor and former member of the improv group The Nellie Olesons.[1][2]

Early life

[edit]

Cantwell was born in Mississippi and raised in Louisiana.[3]

Career

[edit]

Cantwell appeared in the film Legally Blonde and the TV shows Dharma & Greg, Pushing Daisies, and Will & Grace.[4]

Love Connie has a WOW Presents Plus comedy series called Connie-wood.[5] Love Connie was a special guest on the RuPaul's Drag Race episodes "The Draglympics" (2019) and "50/50's Most Gagworthy Stars" (2023).
